      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DODGEM DASH (1) boasts an excellent record and yet to miss the frame including one wins, the latest hitting the minor money when third (24.60) over 407m at Rockhampton. Looks a key player drawing the cherry. SOLAR POWER (8) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing fifth (20.00) at Q Straight last time. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Should be about the money. RED HOT TWIST (2) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (20.42) at this track in a Grade 6. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Can find the frame this time. ATOMIC PENNY (3) did a good job to finish second last time out over 352m at this track (20.03) in a Grade 6, the second top-three finish on the trot. Good beginner aided by a handy draw.",
